<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>gēn suí zhǔ de rén wú shù yòu wú míng 迦南206</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 gēn suí zhǔ de rén wú shù yòu wú míng tài yáng xī luò yòu dōng shēng,
 cóng zǎo dào wǎn yī tiān tiān de zǒu guò wǒ men yòng hàn shuǐ gēng yún zhe rén shēng,
 shì shéi ràng nǐ men lí kāi qīn rén, shì shéi ràng nǐ men láo kǔ bēn xī dōng,
 shì yīn yé sū de ài huǒ zài xīn zhōng rán shāo, wǒ men dōu yuàn yì xiàn shàng yī shēng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>206</hymn_number>
</song>